title: We need OTA to support 5G and VoLTE in KUWAIT for Pixel 5
content:
Hi there
(All) 5G phones working just fine here in KUWAIT with 5G network as well as VoLTE. I don't know why google locked it's Pixel 5 !! 
Please we need an OTA to fix this issue .
LTE working just fine but we need the 5G and VoLTE to work like other phones do !

Thanks
